The '''Bunkurd Corporation''' was a corporation that engineered a bacterium that helped break down the huge amount of waste that was produced by [[Galactic City/Legends|Imperial City]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] daily. The waste was converted to a more biodegradable by-product. Even though the bacterium improved Coruscant's sewage problems by twenty-precent, if the bacterium was consumed by [[Human/Legends|Humans]], they would suffer from what would later be known as [[Bunkurd Sewer Disorder]].

[[Ead Vionor]] was a major shareholder in it, until he was assassinated by [[Kylaena]] in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]].

